schemes provide an effective and affordable healthcare service to all citizens including BPL category, rural population.The government is involving of all the communities in healthcare services for increasing accountability in the scheme.These healthcare schemes are being implemented through public-private partnerships to provide choices to the patients among multiple service.Under MSBY, government will provide an health insurance cover to all the uncovered families of the state.Under RSBY, government will cover all the unorganized workers and provide them an health insurance cover.Benefits of (RSBY) & Mukhyamantri Swasthya Bima Yojana (MSBY)There are several benefits of the healthcare schemes which are available for the state residents. Below listed are some of the main benefits of MSBY and RSBY.The beneficiary of both the schemes will get insurance cover of up to Rs. 50,000 per family per annum on a family floater basis (up to 5 members).The beneficiaries also gets cashless treatment in any hospital whether it is a government hospital or private health institution of state or country.Each family will get a Bio-Metric smart card under both the schemes. This card will show codes of each ailment and package cost.The candidate will get both medical and surgical procedures in the hospital.The govt. has included around 1159 surgical procedures that will be handled on a day care basis or the need for hospitalization.Under the Mukhyamantri Swasthya Bima Yojana, Chhattisgarh government provides each family of state an health insurance cover which protect them against the expensive cost of illness. These both schemes will help in mobilizing the funds and increases the efficiency of healthcare services.To get more information about the healthcare scheme, call at 104 toll free or visit the official website at http://rsbycg.nic.in.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}